subSubSection.paragraph:
Habitats and ecology:
A broad habitat and host generalist (
Watters 1997
). In Middle Asia, the species inhabits plain rivers, canals, and ponds with clay-silty bottom; very common (
Izzatullaev and Boymurodov 2016
).
